    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and carpet. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, but it may require some upcoming maintenance to keep it in peak operating shape. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a reasonable price point.",
